Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是如月桃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們是雙胞胎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界上還真有長得這麼相似的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的確是如月桃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你是我的粉絲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然非常感謝你喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過總是粘著我的話 我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.03,0:00:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簽名的話還是可以簽的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我就帶她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 請好好聽人家說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 自我介紹有些遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:00:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫木戶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:00:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(455,437)\fs21}Kido
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:14.91,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0}act 03 目隱code
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴…你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 是嗎 確實太突然了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這要怎麼說明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被一個奇怪的人纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總…之先想辦法逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就單刀直入地問你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有覺得自己不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,例如同學 家人 擦肩而過的路人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和除自己以外的人比較
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感受到自己身為「異質」了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然問那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是從幾歲開始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我逐漸從其他人的意識裡消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人的舉動彷彿建立在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從未存在這一事實之上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是令我難以忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 你和我完全相反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不是你的本意你都會吸引別人目光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經意識到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說了 我是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 無論怎麼想都是木戶你的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只說過為了獲取信任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微使用一下能力如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…大家在商量的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是說過稍微威脅一下的話更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過那種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過嗎 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我倒是不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是木戶的能力把自己變得像幽靈一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然展示給對方看 肯定會嚇到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽…幽靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來茉莉第一次看到木戶能力的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇得都跳起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會被嚇成那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這這這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這難道是綁架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人質！ ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 都怪木戶 事情變得麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 茉莉 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到我們目隱團基地 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目…隱團？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我們可怕的木戶團長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你做了失禮的事情 真是非常抱…歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先做自我介紹 我叫鹿野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,437)\fs21}Kano
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊摔倒的蓬蓬毛是茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(562,437)\fs21}Marry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家才不是蓬蓬毛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後那個一心圍著茉莉轉的大傢伙是瀨戶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(668,437)\fs21}Seto
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那算什麼介紹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 單方面讓你受怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後還帶你到這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然原本就是想讓你過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好像讓你產生了誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我看不出你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 看不出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也看到了木戶的消失能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目隱」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到那個之後就昏過去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿野 你很失禮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說到哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了 能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.46,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到之後有什麼想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說那真的是消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那也不可能是超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…什麼要那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了這個之後還想向你搭話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的報導？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了這個之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是星探什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…難道在演唱會中途換了彩色隱形眼鏡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.07,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木戶也說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說你一直以來都保密眼睛的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小時候就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我記不清具體是什麼時候開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從某個時期開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做的事情都變得異常受人矚目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「目奪」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才成為偶像的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是和木戶完全不同的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開開…都說了是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木戶的能力很厲害也十分可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我什麼都不說了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉那麼吵鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 我真嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到除了我還有人擁有這種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們小時候和如月你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家眼睛都變紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初真的有很多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過幸虧我們能像這樣在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互幫助 才總算撿回了一條命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎 你們關係不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是一段孽緣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就是這樣 如月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力和我們的能力是一樣的沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 根據我們的觀察來看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還沒有熟練使用那種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所說 今天我也狼狽不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 沒有習慣的話就會那樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去木戶也這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這樣下去的話就會消失掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我們想幫你讓你能夠掌握你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能讓你學會控制能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以避免再次發生像今天那樣的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以做到那種事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是做不到 我現在就是空氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.93,0:09:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底什麼時候能學乖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說 如果我能控制好能力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能像普通的女孩子一樣出門購物了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以和朋友聊天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都得看你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我非常希望你能成為團員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至於最後的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那不是你的本意也會實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明交到朋友很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得熱鬧起來 真是不錯的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我泡了茶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目目團
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:53.03,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 再見 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:11:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機…也許不能用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 在什麼都沒有的地方都能摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個笨蛋 會妨礙到我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是茉莉的「目奪」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與她對視之人幾分鐘之內會完全失去行動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…應該不會有生命危險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 好像都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說都是茉莉弄壞了你的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 我的能力可以抵消你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也算是得到了不錯的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧你我有一種變成了透明人的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團長的能力真是厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然可以讓什麼東西都能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:15.22,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,完全…不會…被人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過一旦被人碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,效果就會立刻解除
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實這是將一定距離之內的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對自己的認知無限稀薄的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來它很適合用在小如月身上 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 這件事有必要大家全都來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茉莉 不要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿野 雖然換手機是我自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家要一起來重新買打碎的玻璃杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是事先已經取得大家同意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別生氣嘛 小如月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.31,0:12:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是瀨戶的提案哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得出來買東西還是大家一起比較開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK OK 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼總之先去換手機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我去找店子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊 長得有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實有一點神似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人是你哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不用你管啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鹿野你笑得太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來為什麼他會在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常明明從來不出門的 偏偏今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太糟糕了太糟糕了太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 如月 剛剛那個人是你的哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢…那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是神似呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很囉嗦 請不要管這些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:13:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 趕緊辦完正事回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡可能快的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來情況有些不妙呢 木戶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我們得從樓梯下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥那邊讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之你先待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鹿野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀨戶 你也跟著去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡 她們沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 你要好好跟著木戶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀨戶 緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你也使用能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不太情願 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿野他到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會被抓到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人面對那麼多人 不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常情況下肯定被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他有那種能力 應該不會被抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是笨蛋發過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說面對這種情況為什麼這個人還這麼游刃有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鹿野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好像很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙的能力是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓別人眼中的自己變成另外一副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單來說 就是「目欺」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許他拍這張照片的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在襲擊犯那些傢伙看來他是被綁起來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:16:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是這樣 這傢伙還真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直無可救藥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}Mail 鹿野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}我是鹿野~。我在小如月的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}哥哥身邊，身為人質中！瀨戶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}對我說你們非常擔心、所以就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}發了照片給你們要打起精神來哦~。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}Mail 鹿野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}我說木戶你啊總是說人家是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}笨蛋什麼的不是很過分嗎？儘管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}如此人家還是很危險的啊。稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}擔心一下我也不錯的說~總之為了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}不讓你一個人寂寞先拍了張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}發給你了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}是否刪除？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}已刪除。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼鹿野他聽得到我們說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是他的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是瀨戶因為他擁有竊取別人思想的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他本人非常討厭 很少使用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣看來大家真的很像是超能力者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 貌似至少我們的對話能傳達過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能想辦法打倒他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠各位的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指的是擊退他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是不要抱太大的希望比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們之中還沒有能與持槍的人為敵的武鬥派哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然如此 即使要逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要這個建築的電氣系統還在敵人的把握之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捲簾門也打不開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去也無法帶著你的哥哥逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,況且我哥哥已經被抓住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概想到了一個好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認耳機里傳來了女生的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來和你說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:29.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然小貴音也一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫貴音的是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想…電視裡說的那種超級厲害的黑客之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種感覺的女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看上去 哥哥好像有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿野那裡還發來了其他的內容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要讓你的哥哥瞄準機會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能執行一個成功率100%的秘策
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手上拿的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:18:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器 我也想努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你小子當你揍的是誰的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你倒是說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢 想死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺心跳都要停了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之從這裡開始要慎重一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這關係到人命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子唧唧歪歪說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如月 怎麼樣 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說白了只要把捲簾門打開就行了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概靠我哥哥和另外一個女孩子應該做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然這要和鹿野確定一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要怎麼製造讓你哥哥逃出去的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我多多少少可以感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰在什麼地方做什麼事情可以吸引別人的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以那個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我來創造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看見了 就是那裡的電視
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才應該一輩子待在監獄裡吧 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在裝什麼帥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團長 小茉莉 就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如月桃 16歲 是一位偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類開始畏懼 厭惡怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的人扔石頭 有的人會放火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們用各種各樣的方法襲擊她想要殺死怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「為什麼我一定要遭受這種事情」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每當怪物被人類傷害的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被刺痛的內心深處都會發出陣陣悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從此誕生的恐懼在心中深深紮根變換形態
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知從何時開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物的心中已經堆滿了各種對人類的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.10,0:22:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一種又一種的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.04,0:23:01.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿是在保護怪物一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從內心溢出 改變怪物的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感情得以表現的怪物得到了強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉了很多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次殺死人的那一天 怪物哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.10,0:23:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天也是 第三天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像幼小的少女一樣 不斷地哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,111)\bord0\fs27\shad2}act04:陽炎days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天能好好說出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須趁我還在這裡的時候告訴她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我並不討厭夏天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}コンクリートが揺らいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:36.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}霞み燻む、君の望ている夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}テンプレートをなぞった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}知らないままの日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}ハイテンポなアテンダンス
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:46.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}消えない　足りない　落ち込んだ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:48.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}最終話が来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}言えない　君は泣きそう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:52.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}ほら、目を閉じて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:53.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}迷子なら一緒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}帰り道もないでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:58.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}継ぎ接いでた　秘密に願う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}未来は平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}さぁ、手を鳴らせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:06.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}０で廻った　勘違いを今日も集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.53,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:10.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}君もまた、無我夢中？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「play」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}届くまで叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:13.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「save」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}叶うまで足掻いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}その手を掴むまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}この温度は忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:20.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「daze」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}心を消さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「change」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}一人で泣かないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}「孤独」なら　塗り替えれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:32.81,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}「ひとりぼっち」を変えようとした君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.10,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}混凝土震顫著的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:36.61,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}籠罩在霞光中的 你一直看著的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:38.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}點綴著範式的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.72,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}依然一無所知的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.61,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}快速參與其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.69,0:01:46.26,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不會消失 無法滿足 消沉的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:48.49,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}最終話就要到來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:50.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}說不出這句話的你泫然欲泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:52.32,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}來 閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:53.77,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}我們迷途之人應當一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.75,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}你也沒有歸宿之處對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:58.99,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不斷接續著 悄悄地許願
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}未來是平凡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.02,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}來 擊掌為證
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:06.41,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}今天也從零開始聚集一切誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.53,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:10.35,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}你是否也迷途夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:11.12,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「play」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.78,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}吼叫到傳達給你為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:13.57,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「save」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.23,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}掙扎到實現為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.62,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}直到緊握住那隻手為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.18,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}我不會忘記這份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:20.82,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「daze」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.46,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不要消卻真心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.24,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}Let's 「change」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.04,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}不要獨自哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.24,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}「孤獨」什麼的 是可以重寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:32.81,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\be6}與想要不再「一人獨處」的你在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:57.05,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}意味のないままで　期間は過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:06.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}理解しようとして　気づいた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:14.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}遠く離れた笑え声なんも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:21.83,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}どこにも聞こえない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:27.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}涙が落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:32.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}これが未来だというならいっそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:37.53,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}やりきってない明日を手放して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:43.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}声の聞こえない場所に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:47.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}一人でいよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:52.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}暮れる世界の涙を知って
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:58.20,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}溢れ出す理不尽を数えても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:14.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}こんな日々を　おくる意味はきっと見つけられないなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:57.05,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}毫無意義的日子裡 期限卻已過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:06.86,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}想要去理解 卻察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:14.89,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}分隔在遙遠之地的笑聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:21.83,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}在哪裡也聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:27.20,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}眼淚都落下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:32.71,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}如果這就是未來的話 還不服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:37.53,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}果敢地放棄還沒有到來的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:43.38,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}在聽不見聲音的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:47.41,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}一個人靜一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:52.50,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}就算知道逝去世界的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:58.20,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}就算列舉溢出的荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:14.58,EDCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\be3}這樣度過每一天的意義 最後也一定不會找到
